thread.title: Tesla issues another Cybertruck recall, making 6th this year

author: kalb.com
title: Tesla issues another Cybertruck recall, making 6th this year
text:
(CNN) – Another recall has been issued for Tesla’s Cybertruck drivers.
The National Highway Traffic Safety Administration said the recall involves a faulty part that could cause the vehicle to lose power, impacting the wheels.
The recall applies to 2,400 vehicles built between Nov. 6, 2023, to July 30, 2024.
Tesla said it isn’t aware of any accidents, injuries or fatalities due to the issue so far.
This is the sixth recall for the Cybertruck this year.
